<table><tr><td>National Clinical Guideline Centre. Atrial fibrillation: the management of atrial fibrillation.  London (UK): National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE); 2014 Jun. 49 p.&nbsp;(Clinical guideline; no. 180).&nbsp;</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712194047/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48333&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.nice.org.uk%252fGuidance%252fCG180">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712194047im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
